---
description: Python standards
globs: ["src/**/*.py", "tests/**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: false
---
- Python 3.11+, full type hints, Pydantic models for IO and settings.
- Prefer httpx (async) for HTTP; respect timeouts and retries with backoff.
- Keep functions small and pure where possible; isolate side effects.
- Write pytest tests alongside features. Mock external services (NCBI, LLM providers) in unit tests.
